;World War II
*Ernest Purnell Hill;
*Rupert Whalley.

The following officers commanded the 58th/59th Battalion:<ref name=AWM2/>
*Rupert Whalley;
*Arthur Palmer;
*Patrick Starr;
*George Warfe;
*Hyde Sweet;
*William Mayberry.

